        "body": "Description\nThe footer section of the website contains multiple links under the Contact and Credits columns. Currently, these links do not have any hover animation or visual feedback, making the user experience less interactive.\n\nRequested Enhancement:\nApply a consistent hover effect to all footer links.\n\nThe effect may include:\n1. Color change\n2. Underline animation\n3. Smooth transition\n4. Any modern interactive hover style\nExpected Outcome:\nWhen a user hovers over any footer link, it should visibly react with the chosen hover style, improving UI clarity and overall user experience.",
